{"tha-ap109:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap109:0.2":"Bhikkhadayivagga ","tha-ap109:0.3":"Nalamaliyattheraapadana ","tha-ap109:1.1":"“Padumuttarabuddhassa, ","tha-ap109:1.2":"lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap109:1.3":"Tinatthare nisinnassa, ","tha-ap109:1.4":"upasantassa tadino. ","tha-ap109:2.1":"Nalamalam gahetvana, ","tha-ap109:2.2":"bandhitva bijanim aham; ","tha-ap109:2.3":"Buddhassa upanamesim, ","tha-ap109:2.4":"dvipadindassa tadino. ","tha-ap109:3.1":"Patiggahetva sabbannu, ","tha-ap109:3.2":"bijanim lokanayako; ","tha-ap109:3.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap109:3.4":"imam gatham abhasatha. ","tha-ap109:4.1":"‘Yatha me kayo nibbati, ","tha-ap109:4.2":"parilaho na vijjati; ","tha-ap109:4.3":"Tatheva tividhaggihi, ","tha-ap109:4.4":"cittam tava vimuccatu’. ","tha-ap109:5.1":"Sabbe deva samagacchum, ","tha-ap109:5.2":"ye keci vananissita; ","tha-ap109:5.3":"Sossama buddhavacanam, ","tha-ap109:5.4":"hasayantanca dayakam. ","tha-ap109:6.1":"Nisinno bhagava tattha, ","tha-ap109:6.2":"devasanghapurakkhato; ","tha-ap109:6.3":"Dayakam sampahamsento, ","tha-ap109:6.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap109:7.1":"‘Imina bijanidanena, ","tha-ap109:7.2":"cittassa panidhihi ca; ","tha-ap109:7.3":"Subbato nama namena, ","tha-ap109:7.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap109:8.1":"Tena kammavasesena, ","tha-ap109:8.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap109:8.3":"Maluto nama namena, ","tha-ap109:8.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati’. ","tha-ap109:9.1":"Imina bijanidanena, ","tha-ap109:9.2":"sammanavipulena ca; ","tha-ap109:9.3":"Kappasatasahassampi, ","tha-ap109:9.4":"duggatim nupapajjati. ","tha-ap109:10.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap109:10.2":"subbata atthatimsa te; ","tha-ap109:10.3":"Ekunatimsasahasse, ","tha-ap109:10.4":"attha malutanamaka. ","tha-ap109:11.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap109:11.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap109:11.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap109:12.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma nalamaliyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap109:13.1":"Nalamaliyattherassapadanam sattamam. ","tha-ap109:13.2":"Sattamabhanavaram. "}